review: I wasn't expecting a movie about Facebook to be this intense, but The Social Network really surprised me...
Mind blowing visuals and a story that bends your brain. Nolan is a genius!
The Martix is a great example of a movie that will live for ever or a very log time. The story and concept are out of this world.
I can safely say that it has been a long LONG time since a movie had this much effect on me after watching it.
